  <div class="attachment-details">
    <h2 class="title"><a href="/government/publications/local-authority-preparations-for-remembrance-sunday/local-authority-preparations-for-remembrance-sunday">Local authority preparations for Remembrance Sunday</a></h2>
    <p class="metadata">
